ea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974677_3890774000954275_6999002797222852641_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hOvGJEMFWYsQ7kNvgEneQAB&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDs3Hvc45CNtdTAdVclR8StvsKdVCZVaoLbfY7uVOPrEA&oe=6710EF5B"}, "display_name": "X-BOOSTER DEMO", "keywords": [], "long_description": "X-BOOSTER is a fun and innovative way to enjoy an intensive VR full-body workout!\nSelect any of our handcrafted original tracks to get your groove on to and start burning those calories!\nWant to jam out to your own set of tunes? \nNo problem, X-BOOSTER supports your own MP3 files as well. \n\nStand and fight off the pounds in the virtual arena! \nPunch, cut, block, and dodge your way to a slimmer you.\nHit all the beats by moving fast and aiming precise blows with your gloves.\nGrab projectiles by using the shield. \nAvoid obstacles by bending and dodging.\n\nSpeed and strength are also a factor. Punch as hard as you can to get the highest score!\nExtensive statistics show your results and progress. \nMatch the training level to your personal skills: \n - warm-up or train with your favorite workout, \n - for challenges choose the most intense mode, \n - or create your own training and go at your own pace.", "short_description": "X-BOOSTER is a fun and innovative way to enjoy an intensive VR full-body workout! \nStand and fight off the pounds in the virtual arena. Punch, cut, block, and dodge your way to a slimmer you! Start burning those calories with handcrafted tracks or your own MP3 files."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.nivision.org/x-booster-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "NiVision", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.nivision.org/x-booster?lang=pl", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subs